@@TJvPlaylist.Items
Description:
This property contains all the items of the playlist. This list is the real items (with the complete path). You can add/remove everything you want in this list, it will be reflected on the playlist.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvPlaylist.ShowExtension
Description:
Set this property to true if you want the user to see the extension. If you want to hide the extension, leave this property false.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvPlaylist.ShowNumbers
Description:
Set this property to true if you want to see the track number at the beginning of the track.

